# =============================================================================
# Enhanced Blog Automation Crontab Configuration
# 
# Location: /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/cron/blogs.cron
# Purpose: Auto-generate high-quality comprehensive blog posts
#
# Installation:
#   crontab -u govindtank << EOF
#   $(cat /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/cron/blogs.cron)
#   EOF
#
# Or add this line to your system crontab (/Library/LaunchAgents or ~/.crontab):
# =============================================================================

# Enhanced Blog Automation - Generates comprehensive 2000+ char blogs
# Schedule: Daily at 9:30 AM IST (during working hours, before peak traffic)
# Quality-focused: max 3 blogs per run to ensure depth over quantity

# Format: minute hour day month weekday command
# Timezone: Ensure server is in Asia/Kolkata or use absolute times

# Run enhanced blog generation daily at 9:30 AM IST
30 7 * * * /bin/bash /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/scripts/blog-automation/enhanced-blog-cron.sh >> /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/cron/blogs-output.log 2>&1

# Alternative schedules (uncomment as needed):
# 
# # Run twice daily (morning and afternoon)
# 30 7 * * * /bin/bash /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/scripts/blog-automation/enhanced-blog-cron.sh >> /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/cron/blogs-output.log 2>&1
# 30 15 * * * /bin/bash /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/scripts/blog-automation/enhanced-blog-cron.sh >> /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/cron/blogs-afternoon.log 2>&1
#
# # Run every weekday at 9:00 AM IST only
# 0 7 * * 1-5 /bin/bash /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/scripts/blog-automation/enhanced-blog-cron.sh >> /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/cron/blogs-weekday.log 2>&1
#
# # Run once weekly on Sunday at 8:30 AM for batch generation
# 30 7 * * 0 /bin/bash /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/scripts/blog-automation/enhanced-blog-cron.sh >> /Users/govind/hermes_projects/govindtank.github.io/cron/blogs-weekly.log 2>&1

